1
00:00:07,620 --> 00:00:10,340
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:14,300
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:16,980
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:16,980 --> 00:00:19,980
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,380 --> 00:00:24,860
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:25,820 --> 00:00:28,660
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:30,980
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:30,980 --> 00:00:34,820
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:39,500
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:39,860 --> 00:00:43,820
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:50,220
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:54,380
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:54,620 --> 00:00:58,100
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:05,060
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:11,700
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:11,740 --> 00:01:16,700
=Episode 20=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,400
Such insolence!

18
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,720
The late emperor ordered
the cunning Marquis of Zhennan

19
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:23,000
lead troops and build dams

20
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,040
precisely to prevent him

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,080
from digging in here in Feng City
and building his own power base.

22
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:27,800
I never imagined

23
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,720
he'd still collude with Prince Ning
in the end.

24
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:30,920
Your Majesty,

25
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:33,840
the Marquis of Zhennan has been
entrenched in Feng City for years.

26
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,040
His roots run deep.

27
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,720
If he chooses to side with Prince Ning,

28
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:40,480
trying to make a safe withdrawal later

29
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,400
would be extremely risky, I'm afraid.

30
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,520
I implore Your Majesty
to make a swift decision

31
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,840
and return to the capital
to take charge.

32
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,400
Rise now.

33
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,200
Understood.

34
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,280
Yunzhuo,

35
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,720
I think Mr. Wang makes a valid point.

36
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,200
Right now, the area around Feng City

37
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,280
is completely under the Marquis
of Zhennan's sphere of influence.

38
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,800
The moment he pledges loyalty
to Prince Ning,

39
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,120
our position here
will become extremely dangerous.

40
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,400
It doesn't matter.

41
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,360
Don't tell me you actually believed

42
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:07,480
that my purpose in leaving the capital
this time

43
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,840
was merely to fool Prince Ning

44
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,320
and draw the snake out of its hole?

45
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,520
Could it be that Your Majesty has
a hidden card to play?

46
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,320
I intend to use this affair in Feng City

47
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,200
to distinguish the loyal
from the treacherous in my court,

48
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:23,160
and to root out
Prince Ning's entrenched influence

49
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,440
once and for all.

50
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,360
But...

51
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,600
No "buts."

52
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:27,840
Throughout the entire court,

53
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:30,000
Prince Ning controls the channels
through which reports reach me.

54
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,480
If I return to the capital now,

55
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,920
I'll simply be turned back

56
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:35,120
into a puppet emperor,
blindfolded and deafened.

57
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,000
Yunzhuo,

58
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,800
what exactly is your hidden card, then?

59
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,760
My hidden card?

60
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,200
Naturally, it's the well-known
worthless live-in son-in-law,

61
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:44,240
Li Yunhe.

62
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,480
Mr. Li,

63
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,320
this Gambiered Silk truly lives up

64
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,160
to its name as a legendary product
here in Feng City.

65
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,080
Wearing it,
it's so light and breathable,

66
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,040
incredibly comfortable.

67
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,000
Mr. Li,

68
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,040
do you like it?

69
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,240
Of course I like it.

70
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,400
But we'll need far more people
to like it as well.

71
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,800
Can I truly get Gambiered Silk

72
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,520
reinstated as an imperial tribute

73
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,800
just by myself?

74
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,840
Relying on you alone is,
of course, not enough.

75
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,520
We'll need everyone's combined effort.

76
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,000
Chunxiang.

77
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,400
Don't be so shy.

78
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,320
Come on out.

79
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,040
Mr. Li,

80
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,280
I feel like this outfit

81
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,520
is just a bit too form-fitting.

82
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,120
Isn't it a little improper?

83
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,440
Give us a spin.

84
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:39,160
Not bad.

85
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:41,280
That's exactly the effect
I was going for.

86
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,800
But I still feel like

87
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,440
this outfit...

88
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,640
Forget what you feel.

89
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,240
What matters is what others think.

90
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,200
This is a style I designed

91
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,080
specifically for you.

92
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,400
Chunxiang,

93
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,760
Mr. Li is absolutely right.

94
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,120
In this outfit,

95
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,440
your graceful figure
is fully on display.

96
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,840
Walking down the street,

97
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,920
you'd dazzle countless
talented young gentlemen.

98
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,000
Really, Xue?

99
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,840
Your beauty

100
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,240
is a gift from the heavens.

101
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,000
You should display it
with confidence and grace.

102
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,240
Don't ever be shy about it.

103
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,000
Alright. I'll do my best.

104
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,440
Oh, by the way, Mr. Li,

105
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,400
you designed this outfit for me,

106
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,400
and what about my lady?

107
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,760
Naturally, I designed

108
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,000
a whole collection

109
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,000
just for her as well.

110
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:18,120
But those designs...

111
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,640
They're for my eyes only.

112
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,800
Not exactly for public display.

113
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,360
Why not?

114
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,680
Chunxiang, don't listen to his nonsense.

115
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,000
A whole collection just for her?

116
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,640
When a man

117
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,400
sets his heart on the woman he loves,

118
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,880
who knows what goes on
in that head of his?

119
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,600
Well, Mr. Li.

120
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,360
There's something I wanted to ask you.

121
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,600
What is it?

122
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,680
You gave that Gambiered Silk to Ms. Sun,

123
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,960
clearly hoping that she would

124
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,600
rope all of us girls

125
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,000
into promoting the Gambiered Silk.

126
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,200
But for something like Gambiered Silk,

127
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,480
can having us from Chunfeng Pavilion

128
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,600
do the promotion for you

129
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,600
really leave a good impression?

130
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,880
You ladies

131
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,640
really sell yourselves too short.

132
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:57,400
Having the ladies of Chunfeng Pavilion
help me promote

133
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,120
is merely one piece of my overall plan.

134
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,760
Let's go.

135
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,000
It's about time

136
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,200
to get ready

137
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:05,840
for rehearsal.

138
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,080
Rehearsal?

139
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,800
The grand Gambiered Silk showcase

140
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,880
is the huge super-show I've designed.

141
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,480
How could we possibly go on stage

142
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,800
without rehearsing and preparing?

143
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,440
Relax.

144
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,280
With me here,

145
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,400
nothing can go wrong.

146
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,280
Let's move.

147
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:27,300
(Feng City Milk Pudding)

148
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,400
Alright.

149
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,480
(Feng City Milk Pudding)
Take these and hand them out.

150
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:34,620
(Feng City Milk Pudding)

151
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:40,640
You want me to go out on the street

152
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:41,800
and hand these out to people?

153
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,600
(I'm the Emperor of Daqian,)

154
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,120
(the honored sovereign of the throne.)

155
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,520
(And you want me to go
hand out flyers in the street?)

156
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,920
(Delicious and cheap!)

157
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,680
(A price that can't be beat!)

158
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,240
(Delicious and pricey!)

159
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,240
(Not a bargain)

160
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,520
(in the slightest!)

161
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,840
(Feng City Milk Pudding)
(Delicious and pricey.)

162
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,640
(Feng City Milk Pudding)
(Not a bargain in the slightest.)

163
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,920
(Delicious and pricey.)

164
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,720
(Not a bargain in the slightest.)

165
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:07,920
Yunzhuo,

166
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:10,240
Li Yunhe is just too good
at tormenting us.

167
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,400
Honestly, I think you should just
go back to the capital.

168
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,880
Go back to the capital? What for?

169
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,880
Oh, you think you've got nothing to do,
is that it?

170
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,040
See this?

171
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,200
Go put it on.

172
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,240
You actually want me
to parade around in public

173
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,120
wearing something like this?

174
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,600
What's wrong with this outfit?

175
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:24,480
This is

176
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,400
a custom-tailored,
haute couture piece I made for you.

177
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,000
It suits your temperament perfectly.

178
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,800
Hurry, put it on.

179
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,080
No way.

180
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,640
I

181
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,040
refuse.

182
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,600
You actually dare refuse?

183
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,680
Zhao Ziyao, don't forget,

184
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,400
this entire Xianquan Tavern

185
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,520
now belongs to me.

186
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,440
If you won't do the work,

187
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,200
I can make you homeless in a heartbeat.

188
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,280
Look,

189
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:49,400
I don't have time
to give you a motivational speech.

190
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,280
Put it on, now.

191
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,160
Yunzhuo!

192
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,320
Look what he's doing!

193
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,800
Don't throw a tantrum.

194
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,920
Just do as he says.

195
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,920
Go and change.

196
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,200
So disobedient.

197
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,280
Li Yunhe,

198
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,400
you've gone too far!

199
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,280
How could you design

200
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,200
an outfit like this for me?

201
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,440
Oh, my.

202
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,640
You know what?

203
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:14,000
Even though you normally come across
as fierce and prickly,

204
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,120
once you put on
this Gambiered Silk suit,

205
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,880
you've got this added touch
of ethereal grace.

206
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,240
You look just like

207
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,920
a goddess
descending to the mortal world.

208
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,280
Really?

209
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,000
You think

210
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:28,200
I look like a goddess
descending to earth in this outfit?

211
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:28,800
No.

212
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,920
I can't just say
you're "like" a goddess.

213
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,480
You are

214
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,280
a goddess.

215
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,000
Yunhe,

216
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:38,840
so

217
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,800
who do you think

218
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,640
is more beautiful,

219
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,000
me or Yu?

220
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,120
Uh, well...

221
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,920
Li Yunhe.

222
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,520
Mrs. Zhou.

223
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,720
Li Yunhe,

224
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,680
you're not going to make Mrs. Zhou

225
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,720
a model for you too, are you?

226
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,400
Please go ahead,

227
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:08,840
Mrs. Zhou.

228
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,720
I'll trust you this once then.

229
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,240
I hope this method of yours truly works.

230
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,800
How could once possibly be enough?

231
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,200
In the days to come,

232
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,920
I'll still need to rely on you,
Mrs. Zhou.

233
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,800
Wasn't it just supposed to be
one painting?

234
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:23,200
Since we're all here already,

235
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,720
why not paint
to your heart's content in one go?

236
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,000
Fine.

237
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,040
It's done.

238
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,560
What a masterpiece!

239
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,880
Your skill with the brush, Mrs. Zhou,

240
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,280
could rival the imperial court painters.

241
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,800
I'm old now, not as good

242
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,520
as I once was.

243
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,800
What are you doing?

244
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,520
Your job's not finished yet.

245
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,680
Change your pose.

246
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:10,520
I want to see

247
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,120
the portrait
Mrs. Zhou painted of me too.

248
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,320
Forget about that.

249
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,280
Just focus on your job.

250
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,240
Li Yunhe,

251
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,440
have you no conscience?

252
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,520
My legs are practically sore
from all this standing!

253
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,120
I know your legs are sore.

254
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,120
I'll get you an extra chicken drumstick

255
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,400
for dinner.

256
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,400
One measly drumstick
and you think that'll shut me up?

257
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,600
If one drumstick's not enough,

258
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,040
how about two, then? Will that do it?

259
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,400
Any more than that,

260
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,280
and you'll start putting on weight.

261
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,880
Two it is, then.

262
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,200
Li Yunhe,

263
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,600
I've been standing here
for three whole hours.

264
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:45,120
Can't I just sit down for a moment?

265
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,760
Just hold out a little longer.

266
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,720
Stand up straight.

267
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,600
I still have an important announcement
to make.

268
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,320
Stand firm.

269
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,200
Now that's more like it.

270
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,600
Yunzhuo,

271
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:06,520
this is truly a moment
of life-or-death peril.

272
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,080
Whatever comes next,

273
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,800
I'm entrusting everything

274
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,640
to you.

275
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:13,960
Don't make it sound

276
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,680
like Daqian is about to fall.

277
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:17,920
That's just creepy.

278
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,520
What's that attitude?

279
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,400
I'm placing the entire fate of Daqian,

280
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,240
a matter of such gravity,

281
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,880
into the hands of a commoner like you,

282
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:26,120
and you still have
the nerve to complain?

283
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:27,720
Take it.

284
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:31,880
With both hands.

285
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,400
Now that's more like it.

286
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,880
Alright, off you go.

287
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,560
(For the sake of my realm,)

288
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,680
(for the sake of my people,)

289
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,160
(fine,)

290
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:45,960
(I'll endure it.)

291
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,920
What are you still standing there for?

292
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:52,120
(You actually dared
to kick His Majesty?)

293
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:52,920
Get going!

294
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,080
Wang.

295
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,400
You stay here for now.

296
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,040
I've got

297
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:02,720
an important task for you to handle.

298
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,480
- Come here.
- So,

299
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,240
I won't have to go be a shill

300
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,600
and hustle for customers?

301
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,880
Oh,

302
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,600
you're just so short-sighted.

303
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,600
You can't see past your own nose.

304
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,120
Who told you being a shill

305
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,320
is all about dragging in customers?

306
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,480
Then...

307
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:27,000
Next, you just follow my lead.

308
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:28,960
Alright.

309
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,880
Alright.

310
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:32,720
(What kind of wicked scheme
is this brat cooking up now?)

311
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:36,800
(Xianquan Tavern)
Let's go.

312
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,500
- Take it easy!
- Move aside.

313
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,500
Just put it here, right here.

314
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:05,480
Welcome, everyone, to Xianquan Tavern

315
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,800
for today's

316
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:10,400
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk
new collection launch.

317
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:14,080
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk Launch)

318
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:17,000
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk
new collection launch?

319
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,080
What's Xianquan Tavern up to this time?

320
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,400
As the saying goes,
speak not when you eat.

321
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,200
Can't Zhao Yunzhuo

322
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,600
wait until we finish our meal

323
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,920
before he starts messing around
with this stuff?

324
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:26,240
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk?

325
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,600
Fantastic!

326
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:29,520
We've found
the Tang Xian Gambiered Silk!

327
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,200
Go inform the others right away

328
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,440
that Tang Xian Gambiered Silk
is at Xianquan Tavern.

329
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,600
Alright. Now,

330
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,920
let's all take a moment to appreciate

331
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:42,440
this painting.

332
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:47,480
Wow! So beautiful!

333
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:50,040
Wow! What a gorgeous beauty!

334
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:52,200
She's just like the girl of my dreams!

335
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,400
This lady is so divinely beautiful

336
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:57,040
that she's like a celestial maiden
banished from the heavens.

337
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,240
Hey, waiter,

338
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,880
I'll give you a quarter's time

339
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:01,080
to get me the full contact information

340
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,400
of this woman in the painting!

341
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:07,000
I'm sure everyone here
is burning with curiosity right now

342
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:09,600
about the attire this beauty
in the painting is wearing.

343
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:13,000
That's right. What she's wearing

344
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,840
is precisely
the new Gambiered Silk design

345
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:17,200
we're about to launch.

346
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,000
Who cares about
your new Gambiered Silk design?

347
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,680
I want the woman in that painting!

348
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,080
How crude!

349
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:22,960
Don't you even know
that "clothes make the man"?

350
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,280
This beauty looks so transcendent

351
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,280
precisely because she's wearing

352
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:27,200
the new Gambiered Silk design.

353
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:28,880
Enough talk. Boss,

354
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,400
take my money here

355
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:32,240
and bring me
the outfit in that painting.

356
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,520
I want a set too!

357
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:34,400
So what if it costs a bit?

358
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:36,320
I can totally afford that.

359
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,000
I want one too!

360
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,040
- Me too!
- Me too!

361
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,520
Uh, as we all know,

362
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,600
to be selected as a royal tribute,

363
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:48,000
it must be a renowned product
from a specific region...

364
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:02,040
And Gambiered Silk

365
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:04,280
is, of course,
the specialty of Feng City.

366
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:06,720
But

367
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,200
I heard from my second uncle

368
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,840
that Feng City's Gambiered Silk

369
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:11,400
failed to make the selection.

370
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,320
Exactly.

371
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:12,800
(Wait.)

372
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:15,080
(Even these kinds of questions
have the answers right on the flyer?)

373
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:17,080
(Could this guy be another plant)

374
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:19,040
(sent by Li Yunhe?)

375
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,440
That's correct.

376
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,880
Gambiered Silk did have

377
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,040
its royal tribute status revoked.

378
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:31,240
But at a time like this,

379
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:34,840
many people will start to question it,

380
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,640
to criticize and slander it.

381
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:40,440
So we must change people's perceptions

382
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,520
because Gambiered Silk

383
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:44,800
was once the pride of Feng City.

384
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:54,800
I'm willing to stand up
and speak out for Gambiered Silk.

385
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:58,040
Over this period, we visited

386
00:14:58,040 --> 00:15:00,080
over 20 villages and towns,

387
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:04,200
conducted 92 internal research studies,

388
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:07,200
interviewed more than 1,300 people,

389
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,440
and invested ten times the effort,

390
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:11,800
all just to perfect a single garment.

391
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:14,600
(What the heck)

392
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,680
(is all this gibberish written here?)

393
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:17,760
Bravo!

394
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:18,880
Beautifully said!

395
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:20,120
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

396
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,440
- Well said!
- Well said!

397
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,400
- Absolutely brilliant!
- Yeah!

398
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:56,100
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

399
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:59,460
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

400
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:02,700
♪Who took the March rain♪

401
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:06,300
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

402
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:09,460
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

403
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:12,820
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

404
00:16:13,700 --> 00:16:19,620
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

405
00:16:19,660 --> 00:16:23,100
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

406
00:16:23,340 --> 00:16:26,180
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

407
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:28,620
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

408
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:32,820
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

409
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:36,180
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

410
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:39,460
♪In fine liquor,
